article_title: Twerk-Off: Stephen Colbert vs. Miley Cyrus
article_text:
(Photos: Comedy Central | Getty)

Related Articles:

By now you've probably had your fill hearing about Miley Cyrus' grind-fest at last month's MTV VMAs and have moved on to her naked demolition derby of "Wrecking Ball," but Stephen Colbert's still getting solid mileage (pun intended) out of her twerking spectacle. In celebration of the potential repeal of Obamacare, the Colbert Report host borrowed a few moves from the artist formerly known as Hannah Montana, foam finger and all. Did he nail it?I don't know — the bar was set pretty high (or low, depending on how you look at it):
